William Seed, appellee, v. Peoples National Bank & Trust Company et al., defendants, on appeal of Charles Vaitekunas and Tekla Vaitekunas, appellants.Gen. No. 34,506.Heard in the third division of this court for the first district at the June term, 1930.

Friend, J., not participating.

Opinion filed October 29, 1930.Rehearing denied November 10, 1930.Harold O. Mulks, for appellants. Anthony A. Olis, for appellee. Mr. Presiding Justice Wilson

delivered the opinion of the court.
